<div class="col two-sm last" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn2">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Travel information</h3>
    Road informationFrom the M6 motorway use junction 32 off the M6.  Turn left off the slip-road onto the A6 Garstang Road, heading towards Preston. <br/>At the second major set of traffic lights turn left into Sharoe Green Lane. <br/>The main entrance to Royal Preston Hospital is 200yds on the right. <br/>Bus informationPreston Bus Ltd operates services from the main Preston Bus Station to the Royal Preston Hospital. Services required are numbers 7/19/22/23/123. Preston Bus has recently introduced onto the hospital routes buses adapted for use by disabled people to ensure easy access and exit from public transport. For further information please contact Preston Bus Ltd on 01772 821199 or 01772 253671. <br/>Local directionFor directions to Royal Preston Hospital and Sharoe Green Hospital please click on the Directions/Parking link from the Trusts Website - <br/><br/>http://www.lancsteachinghospitals.nhs.uk


</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>The Royal Preston Hospital has eight public car-parks providing 2,020 spaces, there are also 100 spaces for disabled people.  Details of the new charges from July 2017<br/><br/>Up to 30 minutes	FREE<br/>Up to 1 hour		2.50<br/>Up to 2 hours		3.50<br/>Up to 4 hours		5.50<br/>Up to 6 hours		6.00<br/>Up to 8 hours		8.00<br/>More than 8 hours	10.00<br/><br/>The same charges will apply to all carpark users including Blue Badge holders. If Blue Badge holders, or anyone else using our carparks need support to park or obtain a ticket, please contact the carpark team for assistance by pressing the button at the carpark entrance barriers.</p>
